{"tid":1630161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要10月8 成功三罷．就要黨鐵停","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:31:31.000Z","uid":175806,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"898aee9cec55753066fc1d4f45075bb88927bbb1","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7號晚係關鍵！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要令黨鐵全線第二日停駛</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">港豬們好耐未三罷啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人．反抗</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人．三罷</span>"},{"pid":"17d2f12c0fe392a35828e05e2ab3614dc04074cf","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7fe16084e6185a6cf6de15d9a62f0c187b4ce348","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"25e4bd1296c86f9528cfe5fae99a6806739e5ccd","tid":1630161,"uid":287032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:45.000Z","msg":"黨鐵<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">春袋</span></span>係<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控制室同訊號系統</span></span><br />\n好多車站開唔到都係因為控制室維修唔到<br />\n因為所有訊號同指示都係由控制室傳達"},{"pid":"93cd9934cee39ccb5d04eb01df2cdc9e9ab52238","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"一定要搞撚到全港被罷工!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c9b49973153f2c42e913d9271322ab72ff47ad","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"push:("},{"pid":"6e3f3a5578a82819328277fb965f975b91f85a91","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n香港人．<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗</span></span><br />\n香港人．三罷 </span>"},{"pid":"444ff60860f9d5ffdd525946fb03dcd46c5a9eab","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港人．反抗<br />\n香港人．三罷"},{"pid":"412d840bdac3dddf0e0ec54609d1f3c2de8ceaf6","tid":1630161,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"香港人．反抗<br />\n香港人．三罷"},{"pid":"9821ea28f07f8d6c85d7ff3911922a0c4691677d","tid":1630161,"uid":15259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"24ace202564c51a5916336632eeb2282efb65160","tid":1630161,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1490345e8312ea05de5c1d16bdc7847a599270c7","tid":1630161,"uid":262301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a8344fad73fde78001a3d3832bf37fe1ee7767","tid":1630161,"uid":290514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"7號晚搞真係可以收黨鐵皮？<br />\n第二朝翻工，咪又照樣重開<br />\n<br />\n戰略一定要轉<br />\n舊方法，只會帶來舊結果<br />\n真係好想搞得成三罷"},{"pid":"5bc6c7617e079cabe2346930f592bf7c86577e9b","tid":1630161,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"勁推"},{"pid":"a0ed2df3ac4fc9457fb256b213b94d48c55b8fe7","tid":1630161,"uid":128373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:42:07.000Z","msg":"要佢地主動罷工就算數啦<br />\n打撚爆佢交通  咁撚鐘意返  就行返工<br />\n再唔係游水過海囉"},{"pid":"b6bada13406d7b70aed5575a5ebe3656a95aba5f","tid":1630161,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:42:29.000Z","msg":"總之<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚唔休息<br />\n18區要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\ngphone作為sell法案既先導者, 已經叫左大家唔好割裝修/魔法, 因為法案無可能7日通過, 通過亦唔代表有實際壓力可以令我地即贏.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%80%E5%A1%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259D%25BF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A1%258A%2F&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6gPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=87e30c54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259D%25BF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A1%258A%2F&h=7732283f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%80%E5%A1%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>大家緊守崗位，記得四大原則。<br />\n<br />\n10月7日<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<br />\n1. 貼文宣 (全日)<br />\n2. 唱歌 (大家預15:00後)<br />\n3. 追悼會 (19:00，睇日程表)<br />\n3. 國際文宣戰線 (全日)<br />\n<br />\n勇武：<br />\n1. 只針對裝修爛鐵(睇赤鐵情況而定，可在20:00或更早)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https:/